<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM5.8">
<l>tokkilaṅki yāṟellām parantōṭit toṭukaṭalē</l>
<l>pukkaṉṟip puṟamniṟka māṭṭāta maṟṟavaipōl</l>
<l>mikkilaṅku mukilniṟattāy viṟṟuvakkōṭ ṭammāvuṉ</l>
<l>pukkilaṅku cīrallāṟ pukkilaṉkāṇ puṇṇiyaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Again, like all those glistening rivers that join [together], spread, flow and</l>
<l>enter the ocean [that was] dug, unable to stay outside [of it],</l>
<l>O Lord of Viṟṟuvakkōṭu! O You of the colour of exceedingly shiny clouds!</l>
<l>I shall not enter [anything] other than Your gracefulness that shines entering [my heart],</l>
<l rend="indent">see, O holy One!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
